 expect a round-robin before the quarter-finals, semi-finals and medal battles.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"16 men\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1345}, {\"ngram\": \"16 women\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"B-Boys\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"a round-robin\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1432}, {\"ngram\": \"the quarter-finals\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"semi\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1464}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1471}, {\"ngram\": \"medal battles\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each contest involves a best-of-three one-on-one contest and each athlete is given around one minute to perform.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Each contest\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"a best-of-three one-on-one contest\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"each athlete\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"one minute\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no pause between each dance and when both are complete, a panel of nine judges score the B-boys and B-girls on six criteria: creativity, personality, technique, variety, performativity and musicality.\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no pause\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"each dance\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1641}, {\"ngram\": \"a panel\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"nine judges\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1692}, {\"ngram\": \"the B-boys\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1709}, {\"ngram\": \"B-girls\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1721}, {\"ngram\": \"six criteria\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1737}, {\"ngram\": \"creativity\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1749}, {\"ngram\": \"personality\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1762}, {\"ngram\": \"technique\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"variety\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"performativity\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1798}, {\"ngram\": \"musicality\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1813}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is extra emphasis on performativity and creativity (60%), while the other categories combine for 40%.\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1922, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"extra emphasis\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"performativity\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"creativity\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"60%\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"the other categories\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"40%\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The B-Girls and B-Boys' performances are instinctive given they do not know the music ahead of time, making their spontaneous moves even more impressive.\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 2077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The B-Girls and B-Boys' performances\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1960}, {\"ngram\": \"the music\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2009}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2023}, {\"ngram\": \"their spontaneous moves\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA's Victor Montalvo is the favourite in the men's event to win gold, while compatriot Sunny Choi (B-Girl Sunny) will battle it out with Logan Edra (B-Girl Logistx) in the women's competition alongside Lithuania's Dominika Banevic (B-Girl Nicka), who is the 2023 world champion and just 17 years of age.\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2079, \"end\": 2087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999997474724615, \"rank\": 2.524186419462485e-07, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uni